sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.团队.description: The label for category 团队 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.团队.link.message: The team module in APIPark is an efficient collaboration tool designed to create and manage services by team. Through the team module, enterprises can establish different teams based on project needs, with each team independently managing its API services.
sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.团队.link.description: The generated-index page description for category 团队 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.服务.description: The label for category 服务 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.服务.link.message: The service module allows teams to create and manage multiple services, each service can bind multiple APIs. Users can display the service in the service square for subscribers to subscribe as needed. After subscription applications are submitted, they need administrator approval, and upon approval, subscribers can access all APIs under the service. Through this module, teams can flexibly manage and publish APIs, and subscribers can easily access the required services, improving API usage efficiency and team collaboration capabilities.
sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.服务.link.description: The generated-index page description for category 服务 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.应用.description: The label for category 应用 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.应用.link.message: In `APIPark`, **applications** are units used by service subscribers to manage and organize API subscriptions. Each subscriber can create and manage multiple applications, and subscribe to API services on an application basis. In this way, API subscriptions and calls for different projects or business lines can be managed flexibly.
sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.应用.link.description: The generated-index page description for category 应用 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.API Mar.description: The label for category API Market in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.API Mar.message: The service market of the API open platform is a centralized platform for displaying and managing all available API services. It provides developers with a unified interface to browse, search, and subscribe to various API services. The goal of the service market is to simplify the API discovery and usage process, enabling developers to easily find and integrate the required APIs.
sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.API Mar.description: The generated-index page description for category API Market in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.运维与集成.description: The label for category 运维与集成 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.运维与集成.l.message: Operations and Integration module focuses on the stable operation of the platform and seamless integration with systems. It covers cluster management, SSL certificate management, log monitoring and management, OpenAPI management, and other key functions. By monitoring system status in real time, managing certificates and logs, ensuring the system's high availability and security. At the same time, it provides open interfaces for seamless integration with other systems, supporting diverse business needs, and improving operational efficiency and system integration capabilities.
sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.运维与集成.l.description: The generated-index page description for category 运维与集成 in sidebar tutorialSidebar

sidebar.tutorialSidebar.category.组织.link.message: The organization module ensures the security and efficient operation of the system through centralized management of members, roles, and permissions. It achieves refined permission control, ensuring each member can only access and operate within their authorized range, enhancing transparency, and flexibility, optimizing organizational structure, and improving overall operational efficiency.
